In [11]:
boss['salary'] = 12
boss['min'] = 0
boss['max'] = 0
boss.loc[boss[''].str.contains(''),'salary'] = boss[''].str.replace('','').str.split('')
def myfuc(x):
    try:
        return x[-1]
    except:
        return x
boss['salary'] = boss['salary'].apply(myfuc)
boss.loc[boss[''].str.contains('K'),'min'] = boss[''].str.split('-')
def myfuc2(x):
    try:
        return x[0]
    except:
        return x
boss['min'] = boss['min'].apply(myfuc2).astype(int)*1000
boss.loc[boss[''].str.contains('K'),'max'] = boss[''].str.split('-')
def myfuc3(x):
    try:
        x=x[-1]
        return x.replace('K','').split('')[0]
    except:
        return x
boss['max']=boss['max'].apply(myfuc3).astype(int)*1000
# 
boss.loc[boss[''].str.contains(''),'min'] = boss[''].str.replace('/','').str.split('-')
boss.loc[boss[''].str.contains(''),'min'] = boss.loc[boss[''].str.contains(''),'min'].apply(myfuc2).astype(int)*22
boss.loc[boss[''].str.contains(''),'max'] = boss[''].str.replace('/','').str.split('-')
boss.loc[boss[''].str.contains(''),'max'] = boss.loc[boss[''].str.contains(''),'max'].apply(myfuc3).astype(int)*22
# 
boss.loc[boss[''] == '500-1000/','min'] = 500 
boss.loc[boss[''] == '500-1000/','max'] = 1000
boss.loc[boss[''] == '10-20/','min'] = 10*8*22
boss.loc[boss[''] == '10-20/','max'] = 20*8*22
boss.loc[boss[''] == '5-50/','min'] = 5*8*22
boss.loc[boss[''] == '5-50/','max'] = 50*8*22
boss['max'] = boss['max'].astype(int)
boss['min'] = boss['min'].astype(int)
boss['salary'] = boss['salary'].astype(int)
boss[''] = (boss['max']+boss['min'])/2
